{
  "chapter": 48,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十八回「揭发奸谋」中，江别鹤的阴谋逐步得逞。赵香灵在罗九、罗三的怂恿下，将段合肥父女劫入地灵庄，并设下弓箭埋伏准备对付江别鹤与花无缺。然而这一切早在江别鹤算计之中，他早已救出段合肥，并率花无双闯入大厅。罗九、罗三当场翻脸，将全部罪责推给赵香灵与铁无双。铁无双的绿衫弟子也趁机背叛，解剑认罪。赵香灵被逼入绝境时，一个头戴竹篓的神秘「幽灵」现身相助，指点赵香灵当众揭露江玉郎假扮轿夫、劫镖杀人的真相。赵香灵口若悬河地分析了双狮镖局命案的种种疑点，直指江玉郎才是真凶。就在众人被赵香灵的推理震惊之际，铁无双被发现持剑自刎于椅上。幽灵厉声否认铁无双是自杀，暗示另有隐情。全章以江别鹤伪善的悼词与幽灵的怒斥形成强烈对比，悬念丛生。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们现在尽管笑吧，哭的时候可就快到了……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贤昆仲如此大义相助，在下实是没齿难忘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "区区小事，何足挂齿，只是……庄主心中此刻不知是何打算？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，在下只望能将大事化小，小事化无，等到江别鹤来了，将此事好生解释，只要他不再追究，在下便将段合肥放回去也罢了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "事已至此，庄主还想将大事化小事么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道……难道不……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "事已至此，双方已成僵局，庄主再说与此事无关．无论如何解释，江别鹤是再也不会相信的了！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "如此……如此贤昆仲岂非害煞在下了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "我兄弟出生入死，换来的只是庄主这句话么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下一时失言，贤昆仲千万恕罪，只是……在下此刻方寸已乱，委实已没了主意，一切还望贤昆仲多多指教才是。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "不能和，惟有战！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "战？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "正是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但……但那江别鹤与花无缺的武功，在下……在下……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "花无缺与江别鹤纵然武功惊人，但庄主也不必怕他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "庄主岂不闻，不能力敌，便可智敌。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "却不知该如何智取？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "段合肥父女已在庄主之手，江别鹤投鼠忌器，纵然来了，也必定不敢出手的，庄主你可先将他们稳住。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "然后呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "地灵庄兄弟，个个身手俱都不凡，庄主不妨令人在这大厅四面埋伏，准备好强弓硬弩……",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那江别鹤与花无缺只要进了此厅，纵有三头六臂，只怕也难以活着出去了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这算什么狗屁的主意，那江别鹤怎会中计，赵香灵若是听从了这主意，无异将自己的罪又加深了一层。这样江别鹤就算立刻杀了你，江湖中也不会有半个人出来为你说话的了。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_luo_jiu",
      "text": "贤昆仲以为此计真的行得通么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "自然是行得通的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "此计成功之后，天香塘、地灵庄，势必将名震天下，那时只望庄主莫要将我兄弟赶出去就是了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下怎敢忘记两位……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只是……这样做法，万一不成……岂非……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "事已至此，庄主难道还有什么别的主意不成？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事已至此，看来我已别无选择了。常言道：量小非君子，无毒不丈夫，赵香灵也只好和他们拼到底了！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "正是正是，庄主这句话说出来，才真是个英雄本色！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那江别鹤发现段合肥父女被劫后，势必要立刻赶来，我等行事也得从速才是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟们，准备弓箭埋伏，听我掷杯为号，立刻出手！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "埋伏好了，你可请铁老英雄出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "少了铁老英雄，便成不得事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江别鹤的恶计，难道真的无懈可击么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "弟子来迟，盼师父恕罪……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你等虽来了，却也无济于事……此事已非武力可以解决，少时你等切切不可胡乱出手，免得……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "这是你弄巧成拙！自作自受！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "铁老英雄认为这区区埋伏能害得了江某．也未免将江某瞧得忒低了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "这究竟是怎么回事？老夫根本全不知情！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "若未经铁老英雄同意，赵庄主只怕也不敢如此吧？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "赵香灵，你说！是谁叫你用这卑鄙的手段的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟只道铁老前辈与赵庄主乃是英雄，是以不远千里而来，谁知两位竟使出如此卑鄙的手段来……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我兄弟虽然不才，却也不屑与此辈人物为伍，从此以后，'地灵庄'无论有什么事，都与我兄弟毫无关系！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位怎可说出这样的话来，这一切岂非都是两位的主意？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_jiu",
      "speaker_name": "罗九",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "好个赵香灵，你竟敢将此事赖在我兄弟头上么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_san",
      "speaker_name": "罗三",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "你纵然百般狡赖，只怕也是无人相信的！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我虽不为己甚，但事到如今，你两人还有何话说？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老夫……老夫……气煞老夫也！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事情未分皂白之前，大家且莫出手！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，师父若不义，弟子便不该相随，各位若能分清大义所在，天下武林中人对各位都必将另眼相看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但此事究竟如何，还……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此事事实俱在，你们还有什么不信的？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "text": "师父你休怨弟子无情，只怨你老人家自己做出了此等天理不容之事，弟子为了顾全大义，也只有……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除了铁无双与赵香灵外，此事与各位俱都无关，只要各位不助纣为虐，江某也必定不会牵连无辜！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "我与你究竟有什么冤仇，你要如此害我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "在下与你虽无怨仇，但为了江湖道义，今日却容不得你！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "text": "好，我知道你为了段合肥，要将赵某除去，但你也莫怪了段合肥此刻也在赵某手里，赵某若死，他也是活不成的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "真的么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "轿子里坐的是什么人，你可想瞧瞧么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "你难道还能逃得了么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "念在他成名也算不易，就让他自己动手了断吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "苍天呀苍天，我铁无双今日一死，怎能瞑目！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_wu_shuang",
      "speaker_name": "铁无双",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁某就站在这里，你们谁若认为铁某真的有罪要取铁某的性命，只管来吧！只怕苍天也不能容你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "多行不义，人人得而诛之，普天之下，谁都可以取你性命，别人若不忍动手，就由我来动手吧！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "江玉郎，你真的敢动手么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "堂堂的江少侠，怎会来做轿夫，你莫非瞎了眼了！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "江玉郎，你瞒得过别人，却瞒不过我。你劫了段家的镖银后，赶回这里假充轿夫，为的是要取铁老英雄的性命，这样江湖中人都只道铁老英雄是死在个轿夫身上，日后纵有要来寻仇之人，也寻不着假仁假义的'江南大侠'父子了……江玉郎呀江玉郎，你父子两人行事当真是千思万虑，滴水不漏！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位听见了么，这厮竟敢说劫镖的乃是江少侠……段老爷子你说这厮是不是胡说八道的疯子？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "speaker_name": "段合肥",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "你这话是从何说起，我镖银第一次被劫，就是江少侠夺回来的，他若是劫镖的人，为何又将镖银夺回？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "text": "镖银第一次被劫，本是'双狮镖局'与江玉郎串通好的，江玉郎若不将镖银送回，他们还是要赔出来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "speaker_name": "段合肥",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "他们为何要如此做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此做法，不但提高了江玉郎在江湖中的声望，而且……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "speaker_name": "段合肥",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "而且怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "而且第二次镖银被劫时，别人就再也不会怀疑到江玉郎头上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "speaker_name": "段合肥",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "如此说来，那'双狮镖局'中的人，又怎会……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这恶计之中，'双狮镖局'里的人，自然不免要做冤死鬼，江玉郎自然要将他们杀死灭口，而且……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_he_fei",
      "speaker_name": "段合肥",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "而且怎样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "双狮镖局上上下下既然死净死绝，那镖银自然就没有人赔了，于是那偌大一批镖银，就太太平平落入了'江南大侠'的手中！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "贼咬一口，入骨三分，你临死居然还要反噬，我却容不得你！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好武功！好身手……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "花公子为何要……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论是谁有话要说，咱们都该听他说完了才是，咱们纵然不信他的话，却也得让他有说话的自由，是么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "你无端说出这话，可有什么根据？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "双狮镖局中的人，俱是仓猝而死，连一招都不及还手，而这江南双狮武功并不算弱……在下请问花公子，就算以花公子这样的武功，要想将这些人全都杀死，也不能令他们全都还不了手的，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，就算武功比我更强的人，纵然能制他们于死，只怕却也不能令他们全都还不了手的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但普天之下，武功更强于公子之人，只怕已没有了，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "纵有也不会多。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是以此事只有一个解释。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "什么解释？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这必定是一个与李氏双狮极熟的人下的手，他们万万想不到这人会向自己人下毒手，是以猝不及防，连还手俱都不及……这不问可知，自然除了江玉郎外再无别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 384
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "但据那仅存的活口马夫所见，下手的乃是个威猛老人。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "易容之术，在今日江湖中，虽仍是奥秘，但会的人却也有不少，他既能假充轿夫，为何就不能改扮成威猛老人……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他故意留下那马夫，正是要借那马夫之口……否则他杀人之后，又怎会狂笑而出，否则以他的武功，那马夫就算躲藏，又怎能逃得过他的耳目？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有那马夫逃生之后，立刻就将此事绘形绘影的说了出来，而且说的有声有色，巨细不漏，试问一个真的受了如此惊骇的人，说话又怎会如此明白清楚，所以……那马夫想必也是他的同谋，早已经他指点……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "你说的话又是谁指点你的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这全是我自己想出来的，我……",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "赵香灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对了，我方才说错了，那'马夫'说不定就是现在这'轿夫'，就是江玉郎，而动手的却是江别鹤！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": "char_zhao_xiang_ling",
      "text": "我本不愿与你一般见识，但你既如此胡言乱语，我却也容不得你了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你认得我么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_you_ling",
      "text": "你……你是谁？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你不认得我，我却认得你……我死也不会忘记你！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_you_ling",
      "text": "你……你究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "我早已告诉过你，我不是人，是鬼！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_shan_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "绿衫少年",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀，不好！我师父……我师父……他老人家竟自杀了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_bie_he",
      "speaker_name": "江别鹤",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "铁无双不愧是英雄，勇于认错，他这样一死，生前的罪孽与污名总算已可洗清了！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_you_ling",
      "speaker_name": "幽灵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "放屁！铁无双绝不是自杀的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 48,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    }
  ],
